3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper formulates an optimization problem to minimize the system outage probability, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses the performance analysis of the proposed scheme and compares it with existing schemes using simulation results. This falls under the domain of multimedia. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper proposes an optimal combining scheme and derives the expression for the system outage probability, which involves mathematical optimization and analysis. This falls under the domain of computational engineering, finance, and science.
